---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About The Daily Algorithm.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-3">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-950 dark:text-zinc-50 mb-4">The Daily Algorithm</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-10">Professional technology journalism.</p>
    <div class="tda-prose">
      <p>The Daily Algorithm is an independent technology journal dedicated to covering the algorithms, systems, and decisions shaping the digital world.</p>
      <p>We believe technology deserves rigorous, honest analysis — not hype. Every article is written with clarity, depth, and a commitment to keeping readers informed about what actually matters.</p>
      <h2>Our Focus</h2>
      <p>From artificial intelligence and machine learning to software architecture, developer tools, and the business of technology — we cover the full spectrum with a thoughtful, professional lens.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For editorial inquiries, reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@thedailyalgorithm.com">hello@thedailyalgorithm.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>